import React from 'react'
import {
  SideBarContainer,
  Icon,
  CloseIcon,
  SideBarLink,
  SideBarWrap,
  SideBarWrapper,
  SideBarMenu,
  SideBarBtn,
} from "./SideBarElements";

export const SideBar = () => {
    return (
        <SideBarContainer>
            <Icon>
                <CloseIcon/>
            </Icon>
            <SideBarWrapper>
                <SideBarMenu>
                    <SideBarLink to='about'>
                        About
                    </SideBarLink>
                    <SideBarLink to='discover'>
                        Discover
                    </SideBarLink>
                    <SideBarLink to='services'>
                        Services
                    </SideBarLink>
                    <SideBarLink to='signup'>
                        Sign-up
                    </SideBarLink>
                </SideBarMenu>
                <SidaBtnWrap>
                    <SideBarRoute to="/signin">Sign In</SideBarRoute>
                </SidaBtnWrap>
            </SideBarWrapper>
    </SideBarContainer>);
}

export default SideBar
